description:
Fast transactional table style document NoSQL application database. zero configuration, no dependencies, copy and run, traditional table with unstructured data.
Features:
* CRUD
* Primary key
* Unique and non-unique indexes.
* Unique and non-unique composite indexes.
* SQL like query language
* Transactions support
* Concurrency control, thread safe
* Memory management
* Hot MasterSlave and MasterMaster replications
* On disk and in memory databases supported
* Automatically create databases
* Zero configuration, copy and run, purely managed code
* Dynamic columns
* Different types with different indexes can be stored in same table
* Persistence + ORM + Cache + Embeddable, ONE STOP solution
* ResultSet compatible with LINQ
* High performance, no dependencies
* Update Increment
* Selecting Tracer
For C# Mono Xamarin Windows Phone Silverlight .NET ASP.NET Cross Platform
title: iBoxDB Fast NoSQL Application Database
